5. Get user dues:

GET  : https://arpita-sinha-split-the-bill.herokuapp.com/api/events/getdues
Put "token" from above in header of http as "authorization"

Request : Empty
Response: {
    "dues": [
        {
            "event_name": "Lunch",
            "email": "user1@abc.com",
            "username": "user1",
            "amount_to_pay": 15
        },
        {
            "event_name": "Lunch",
            "email": "user1@abc.com",
            "username": "user1",
            "amount_to_pay": 15
        }
    ]
}



